Hi Coke Studio Bangla!
I have a song suggestion. Ek Hariye Jawa Bondhu by Shayan. So far I have heard only the acoustic version of this song. The song lyrics is really touchy. I think a nice music composition will make that song more touchy and beautiful. I have been following Coke Studio Pakistan and India and observed how they retouched a song and made that more beautiful. I believe Coke Studio Bangla can do that too. Best of luck.
snippet.textOriginal:
Hi Coke Studio Bangla!
I have a song suggestion. Ek Hariye Jawa Bondhu by Shayan. So far I have heard only the acoustic version of this song. The song lyrics is really touchy. I think a nice music composition will make that song more touchy and beautiful. I have been following Coke Studio Pakistan and India and observed how they retouched a song and made that more beautiful. I believe Coke Studio Bangla can do that too. Best of luck.
